《'''伊朗伊斯兰共和国宪法'''》<ref>{{Cite web|title=قانون<!-- Bot generated title -->|url=http://mellat.majlis.ir/archive/1383/10/15/law.htm|accessdate=2006-12-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061207205624/http://mellat.majlis.ir/archive/1383/10/15/law.htm|archivedate=2006-12-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Constitution|url=https://en.parliran.ir/eng/en/Constitution|accessdate=2020-09-01|work=Islamic Parliament of Iran|publisher=Parliran.ir|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203072627/https://en.parliran.ir/eng/en/Constitution|dead-url=no}}</ref>（{{Lang-fa|قانون اساسی جمهوری اسلامی ایران}}）通稱《'''伊朗憲法'''》，是1979年12月2日至3日經公民投票通过的憲法，<ref name="Davari2004">{{Cite book|last=Mahmood T. Davari|title=The Political Thought of Ayatollah Murtaza Mutahhari: An Iranian Theoretician of the Islamic State|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oYHi4AfofW8C&pg=PA138|date=2004-10-01|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-134-29488-6|pages=138|access-date=2020-10-29|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729162443/https://books.google.com/books?id=oYHi4AfofW8C&pg=PA138|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="Eur2002">{{Cite book|last=Eur|title=The Middle East and North Africa 2003|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4CfBKvsiWeQC&pg=PA414|date=2002-10-31|publisher=Psychology Press|isbn=978-1-85743-132-2|pages=414|access-date=2020-10-29|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729165526/https://books.google.com/books?id=4CfBKvsiWeQC&pg=PA414|dead-url=no}}</ref>同時1906年通過的《[[1906年波斯憲法|1906年波斯憲法]]》失效。<ref>[http://www.nyulawglobal.org/globalex/iran.htm Constitutional Background] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nyulawglobal.org/globalex/iran.htm |date=20120107082546 }} ''Hauser Global Law School Program''</ref>1989年7月28日，[[1989年伊朗憲法公民投票|1989年伊朗憲法公民投票]]後伊朗當局對憲法進行修訂。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Constitutional Background|url=http://www.oefre.unibe.ch/law/icl/ir__indx.html|accessdate=2006-09-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060908083917/http://www.oefre.unibe.ch/law/icl/ir__indx.html|archivedate=2006-09-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>伊朗伊斯兰共和国宪法既有[[伊斯蘭神學|伊斯蘭神權]]色彩的一面，也有民主的一面。例如該憲法第一条和第二条規定[[安拉|安拉]]具有統治和立法大權，而第六条又规定总统和议会由民众选举产生<ref name="Fukuyama">{{Cite web|title=Francis Fukuyama: Iranian constitution democratic at heart - WSJ|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970203946904574300374086282670|author=Francis Fukuyama|date=2009-07-28|work=WSJ|accessdate=2020-10-29|archive-date=2017-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027080206/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970203946904574300374086282670|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 但是憲法也規定[[宪法监护委员会|宪法监护委员会]]擁有法律最終解釋權，[[伊朗最高领袖|伊朗最高领袖]]擁有最高權力。<ref>{{Cite web|title=A Detailed Analysis of Iran’s Constitution - World Policy Institute|url=http://www.worldpolicy.org/blog/2010/10/12/detailed-analysis-iran%E2%80%99s-constitution|accessdate=2012-01-16|work=worldpolicy.org|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506150238/http://www.worldpolicy.org/blog/2010/10/12/detailed-analysis-iran%E2%80%99s-constitution|archivedate=2014-05-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

